             was indicted for <rs id="t18231203-171-off916" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18231203-171-off916" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18231203-171-off916" type="offenceSubcategory" value="grandLarceny"></interp>
               stealing, on the <rs id="t18231203-171-cd917" type="crimeDate">20th of October</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18231203-171-off916 t18231203-171-cd917"></join>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18231203-171-off918 t18231203-171-cd917"></join>, a mahogany case, value 1 s.; four watches, value 12 l.; four pair of ear-rings, value 20 s.; four purses, value 3 s.; eighteen combs, value 10 s., and a pencil-case, value 10 s.
            </rs>, the goods of 
               
                  <persName id="t18231203-171-victim1511" type="victimName">
                     Daniel 
                     Burgess
                  <interp inst="t18231203-171-victim1511" type="surname" value="Burgess"></interp>
